Wash rinse repeat for 10 frickin minutes.<br>
<br>
Honestly, there is no game there. Fights have been broken down into mathimatical formulas where there is NO actual need for thought. A computer program could do the job of the best cleric in the game better then he himself could. The healing structure of this game take no ability to think or analize a situation or improvize, just pure timing of clicking buttons. If you think that is a good thing then I am not sure what to say.<br>
